3f36efec04fc693272d71","tid":2253232,"uid":269452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:49:01.000Z","msg":"歷史有邊次發動戰爭唔係為利益㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922a2189176991ca6d4823b905cb99e813fe57a0","tid":2253232,"uid":209153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VV9dc7L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVV9dc7L.gif&h=2df571f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"070ba030a97dc51af42d069608bb26a7992ad289","tid":2253232,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"支持中國即刻出兵<br />\n唔出就係支那廢物"},{"pid":"86d7e7e705a475c3e49c8e7e3c00ae6f2d23c51b","tid":2253232,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"1個攻台理由 唔攻台<br />\n同<br />\n10億個攻台理由 唔攻台<br />\n<br />\n有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3400f3f81402d5a590c61f132cfdae0bb2719db2","tid":2253232,"uid":256517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"855500e664933ad26dd10cfe8e796cd3c802fc8b","tid":2253232,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=835312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D835312&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=8054e025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D835312&h=dd1f3921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=835312</a><br />\n近來美中對抗加劇，台海局勢日趨緊繃，中共解放軍更頻繁派軍機騷擾我國，讓各界憂心兩岸戰火可能一觸即發。然而，中國卻在昨（21）日公布《中華人民共和國國防法（修訂草案）》，增訂可以因為「發展利益」遭受威脅時，發動戰爭或進行全國總動員。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據中國人大網公布的《國防法（修訂草案）》，其中第八章是關於「官方進入國防動員和戰爭狀態」，本次修訂將原本的第44條「中華人民共和國的主權、統一、領土完整和安全遭受威脅時，國家依照憲法和法律規定，進行全國總動員或者局部動員。」增加了「發展利益」4個字，改為「中華人民共和國的主權、統一、領土完整、安全和發展利益遭受威脅時，國家依照憲法和法律規定，進行全國總動員或者局部動員。」並將條次改為第47條。<br />\n<br />\n根據《ETtoday新聞雲》報導，中國國防部長魏鳳和表示，隨著全球局勢、國情、黨情、軍情等發展變化，1997年公布施行的國防法已不能完全適應新時代國防和軍隊建設的新任務、新要求，加上中國現在面臨的安全威脅和挑戰更趨複雜，迫切需要對國防政策制度作出相應調整。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《央視》報導，中國國防法於2019年1月啟動修法工程，目前修法草案已經經過國務院常務會議和中央軍委常務會議討論通過，草案正於中國人大網公布，並於10月21日至11月19日徵求各界意見。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以打瑞典"},{"pid":"c5cff2eafb86f57ab28cc8db5ce6bc2fa6bbe88f","tid":2253232,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"所以幾時出兵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a316a475b934c8860ce838fed09c08e21cd9d245","tid":2253232,"uid":336922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1afbf9a94b39210bb9b9689151b5fd84cc01cde","tid":2253232,"uid":24641,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"量子開戰 同時處於打同唔打中間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"寫稿嗰班人都幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知唔會出擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係日日都要寫到好似好想出戰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3b57dc492180b6bef80d787d277b741715971d","tid":2253232,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"我老豆藍到黑都屌支共得把口，唔撚敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c6ce0e433e3e84d57f59ff79b5ba3bd52a4c70","tid":2253232,"uid":378408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:03:21.000Z","msg":"打先算la，打得成我乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af84d06201027d6ae76f42039c7177c8ef8f90cb","tid":2253232,"uid":336922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6c63905e3952db1846903119288233050813149","tid":2253232,"uid":301406,"like":8,"dislike":0,"s